snippet.title: NES Longplay [744] Parasol Stars: The Story of Bubble Bobble III
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Lemmy556

The version of this game I played was marked as a beta version,
which I played instead of the "finished version", because the it has a few graphical glitches, mostly notable on the title screen and the upper part of the ingame screen. The glitches didn't appear on the Beta version at all. -
